title: Georges Seurat Final Study for “Bathers at Asnières” Mug
description:
Mug developed from Georges Seurat’s Final Study for "Bathers at Asnières", 1883, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

A masterpiece from our collection can be enjoyed every day along with breakfast or afternoon tea! A great gift for a teacher or friend.

  • Size: 12 oz.
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 3.75 x 5 in.
  • Box Dimensions: 5.75 x 4.5 x 4.125 in.
  • Material: Porcelain
  • Microwave and Dishwasher Safe
